Gherkin language

Feature- Each Gherkin file begins with a Feature Keyword
Background- used to define steps which are common to all the test in
the feature file
Scenario- Each test is called a Scenario
Given - pre condition
When - actions we need to perform
And - supporting tag
Then - expected results
But - used to add negative comments

Example
    Feature: Login
    Scenario: Valid Login
    Given I navigated to HRMS app
    When I enter valid username
    And I enter valid password
    And I click login button
    Then I am successfully logged in


  What is Framework
